    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d honestly think it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014always garage-kept and meticulously maintained. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new but with a much friendlier price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
