    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2006 Porsche 911 Carrera S in concours-level condition. This example features the M97.01 3.8L flat-six powerplant paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. Performance is sharpened by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone a comprehensive pre-purchase inspection including a clean bore-scope and detailed oil analysis. The chassis remains rigid with resilient bushings, and the factory-spec Brembo monoblock braking system provides exceptional thermal dissipation. A turn-key enthusiast machine for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Full service history included.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
