      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage, and it\u2019s been pampered since day one. No scratches, no spills, just pure driving perfection. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
