      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S represents a pinnacle of the 996 generation, presented in showroom condition. Powered by a 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant, the engine exhibits flawless compression across all cylinders with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, delivering torque to all four wheels via a viscous-clutch AWD system. The widebody chassis remains structurally rigid, featuring an unblemished factory finish and an undersurface free of oxidation. Mechanical highlights include a factory-spec Bilstein suspension and red four-piston Brembo monobloc calipers clamping cross-drilled rotors. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history, this C4S delivers a visceral, analog driving experience with surgical steering precision and a linear power band.",
      "price": 47500.0,
